reviewText: The DVD includes a mildly interesting group discussion with the six filmmakers, and one of the films is so-so, but the other five are unfortunate. It is difficult to believe these 6 were contest winners. Perhaps it was unwise to limit the contest to Oklahoma.
I wonder how they got to market this dvd. The standards of these short is that of film students working on their first ever projects. This must be some sort of a joke. I've been fooled.
